Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们梦想着  改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}杂音中  传来你的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭开我  欢笑之下的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐着  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们渴求着前往未来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却为此在过去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑着的此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午后  品尝着柚子茶和饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来  占卜梦境的后续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会打开多少扇大门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…寻找的东西  究竟在何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这才发现我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快点找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在这里哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约完成了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去…改变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边  请快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人浑身是血倒在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了  请等一下  夏罗大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:58.61,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀旧的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  夏罗被绑架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗她怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧  她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为与犯人交涉成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉？什么交涉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密  你没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这种事是常有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗大小姐  您醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「没关系的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一点都不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐她没事吧  文森特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事  我说过吧  我不会杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们能早点相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就设了个时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个喜欢收集毒药的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他给了我一些罕见的毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就给她俩试了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连艾可都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不确定这解毒剂是否有效的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会听我的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽商先生  我说过我想要那个铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是想要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把那东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,销毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的事  大家都不知道就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个铃铛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为阿比斯的力量才能够具有现实的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  普通的方法是无法破坏它的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,销毁它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那能否定阿比斯力量  并使其消失的疯狂帽商
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前把它销毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那铃铛销毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  马上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后继续活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我要去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能恩准我吗  雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克…我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没必要听他摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你…一直以来寻求的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你活下去的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你满足了吧  文森特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你啦  帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那药给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好人啊  帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  最喜欢这样的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  文森特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种眼神和你的基尔巴特哥哥一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件的责任在于我太弱  没能保护好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍帅也要懂得适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别自作多情  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你？  不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了自己而活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救你  是因为我怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是出了什么事  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会被雪莉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你妈妈杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种话  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想帮上扎克斯哥哥忙  才在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克斯…哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？ 奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗把布雷克叫作「扎克斯哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  以前都是这样叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然他们并不是真正的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像对哥哥那样仰慕着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你为什么会知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雷姆·鲁内特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常来莱因兹华斯家打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和扎克西斯也已经认识十年多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克也有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克这个人怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前起就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前对人更加冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个无论发生什么事都不会笑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你看到了吗  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快死的时候被夏罗大人发现的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙感觉怪模怪样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把那种怪男人作为客人招待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那种事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我  别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像受伤的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了那个男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗大人的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是被雪莉大人那豁达的为人给感化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克西斯也一点点敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在变得能好好露出笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗  你有看到笑脸猫的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前被阿比斯的意志夺走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了它  让我想起许多以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克在寻求一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝也寻求着自己的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯卡叔叔  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家…帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们穿着都很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  奥斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备把我们拐去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有我们才能做到的  重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信是从拉特维吉学校寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉特维吉学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个国家排名前三的全住宿制学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  现在在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们的艾达在上学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾达？那是什么东西  能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有妹妹啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在这封信的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜启  亲爱的叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  今天是指哪天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少写上日期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的牛腰子派很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个啊  我也很喜欢吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心把男生弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  这个小冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PS：我有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  是吗  有喜欢的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事  叔叔我绝对不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？这是紧急事态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被打扮成这样是要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向艾达确认信的内容  我们要直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入学校！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要潜入吗？像平常那样办个手续见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  那样太不浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走贝萨流斯家挖的秘道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  这里没有人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是拉特维吉学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚状况  你就给我认命吧  海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦我  笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯卡大人  学生们走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌  基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变装很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是学生  奥斯卡大人是教师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大叔是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变…是变态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说您都不可能扮成学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了  好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是校内有可疑人物哦  埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟奥兹他们走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹是会好好享受这种状况的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能稍微高兴点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是为此才带我们来这里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就察觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校内是禁止吸烟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算躲起来吸  也是逃不过雪铃的鼻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（snowdrop，雪铃花，有「思念并等待着分别已久之人」的意义）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  风纪委员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下麻烦了  叔叔他们跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为还蛮好玩的  我是没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不觉得你很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么不愿意和妹妹见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝你…有时也很敏锐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊  把我当白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在夸你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是不愿意  能见面是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…我还没做好心理准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹的事我在之前的信里已经有说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是那样  可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为分别时艾达还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定她已经完全不记得我的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…因为…那时到现在已经过了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的样子已经和以前完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…要是他说「这不是艾达」之类的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹不会说那种话的  绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在  请坦然面对想要见面的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是对我说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我  这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是骗人的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…那时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你为什么不能对自己那样说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因…为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许顶嘴！你这人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  你可是我的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该为这件事感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你就是你而感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊  小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大声喊出你是我的仆人这件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快喊啊  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是～艾莉丝的～仆人～」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…达…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和以前一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  快说  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  艾达还记得我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥很高大…很温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都要帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然记忆是会被美化的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更喜欢现在眼前的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说比记忆中矮了点  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能好好陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触摸得到  能说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在…一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都好想见到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然有改变的地方  但也有没变的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我分开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姑娘  给我适可而止一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是我的私有物品  是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动不动就粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你仆人啊  笨蛋兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便弄成你的私有物品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系已经好到能吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘记来这里的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大家谈论的可疑人物就是叔叔你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突然想来看看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你们没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔也是  好久没像这样说话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送的帽子  在用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然在用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艾达送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  我知道你想说什么  不过现在断定还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真的是那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾～达～  叔叔我们呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问一下关于信里写的PS的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？PS？那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙已经做好觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为会让你轻松死掉哦  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  刚才那是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听人家把话说完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奥兹  别丢下我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和叔叔他们走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心  好像回到了从前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…是谁在弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然改编了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这里面的音乐盒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}小鬼你的罪孽实在太深重了的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}只是不想牵连到别人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}纠正主人的言行也是侍从的义务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}说到底这只不过是你的自我满足罢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我会去死的\N如果只有这个方法的话  我不会犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}小鬼你确确实实是个加害者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}明明完全不了解留下的人会有多痛苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  关于某位侍从之死